description: A collection of circles in a thin, rounded triangular formation with the point at the top of the picture; there is also a smaller triangular formation extending from the bottom of the larger formation with the point where the two formations meet. Each circle has a different number in the center denoting how many lines stem from that point. There is a small black triangle at the top of the larger triangular formation and a grayish-off white triangle in the center.

author.name: VertexArchive
